<chapter id="kword-screen">
<title
>I &kword; Ikhusi</title>

<sect1 id="screen-overview">
<title
>Imboniselo engaphaya</title>

<para
>&kword;, njengezininzi <acronym
>GUI</acronym
> udweliso lweenkqubo ezisekiweyo, yahlula ikhusi kwii ariya ezininzi. I ariya nganye yekhusi isetyenziswa ukwenza iqela lemisebenzi esemqoka efanayo . Xa uqala i &kword; ikhusi, yahlulelwe kwii ariya ezine eziphambili:</para>

<orderedlist numeration="arabic"
> <listitem
><para
><link linkend="kde-isakhelo"
>I &kde; ibar yewonga</link
> (esala entla kudweliso lweenkqubo lonke olwenziwa phantsi kwe &kde;).</para
></listitem
> <listitem
><para
><link linkend="da"
>I Menu Bar</link
>.</para
></listitem
> <listitem
><para
><link linkend="mb"
>uxubo lweebar zesixhobo</link
>.</para
></listitem
> <listitem
><para
><link linkend="tb"
>I ariya yexwebhu</link
>.</para
></listitem
> </orderedlist>

<screenshot>
<mediaobject
><imageobject>
<imagedata fileref="screen.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject>
</mediaobject
></screenshot>

<para
><emphasis
><anchor id="kde-frame"/>Ibar yewonga ye KDE.</emphasis
></para>
<para
>I &kde; Ibar yewonga ijikeleze zonke izicelo ezisebenza phantsi kwe &kde;. Xa ufuna iinkcukacha ezininzi, nceda bona i &kde; Isalathisi soMsebenzisi.</para>

<para
><emphasis
><anchor id="mb"/>Imenu bar</emphasis
></para>

<para
>IMenu Bar inikeza unikezelo kuyo yonke eye &kword;imisebenzi ne nketho. Iqela ngalinye le &kword; imenu bar ichazwe kwicandelo elingenawonga: <link linkend="basic-menubar"
>iMenu Bar engundoqo</link
>.</para>

<para
><emphasis
><anchor id="tb"/>Iibar zesixhobo</emphasis
></para>
<para
>Iibar zesixhobo zinikeza iindlela ezimfutshane kwimisebenzi esetyenziswayo elula. &kword; isebenzisa iibar zesixhobo ezisibhozo, ngemisebenzi efanayo edityaniswe ndaweni nye.</para>

<para
><emphasis
><anchor id="da"/>I ariya yexwebhu.</emphasis
></para>
<para
>I ariya yexwebhu iqulathe i:</para>

<variablelist
> <varlistentry
> <term
>Abaphathi abathe tye nabathe nkqo</term
> <listitem
> <para
>Abaphathi bangasetyenziswa ukukunceda ubeke uxwebhu lakho. Xa ufuna ulwazi oluphangaleleyo kubalawuli, bona <link linkend="abaphathi"
>Usebenzisa abaphathi</link
>.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
>Ibar yokurola</term
> <listitem
> <para
>Iibar zokurola zisetyenziswa ukuya ngapha kwe &kword; uxwebhu ngokukhawuleza. I &kword; ibar yokurola isebenza ngokufanayo neebar zonke zokurola kwi &kde; okanye &Windows;.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
>Umkhethi weisthuba</term
> <listitem
> <para
>Oku kusetyenziswa ukukhetha nokubeka izithuba zokumisa kuxwebhu lakho ngokufomata okulula. Xa ufuna ulwazi oluphangaleleyo kwizithub azokumisa, bona icandelo elingenawonga <link linkend="tab-stops"
>Usebenzisa izithuba zokumisa</link
>.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
>Imboniselo yexwebhu</term
> <listitem
> <para
>Le yi ariya yekhusi elisetyenziswayo ukungenisa okubhaliweyo. Ikubonisa indawo engatshintshiyo yakho yexwebhu, kwaye ikuvumela ukunyenyisa izakhelo, khetha okubhaliweyo, kwaye sika ucole okubhaliweyo. </para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> </variablelist>

<variablelist
> <varlistentry
> <term
><link linkend="char-format-toolbar"
>Ibar yesixhobo yefomati</link
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Le bar yesixhobo inemisebenzi eqhelekileyo yokufomata okubhaliweyo kwakho ne mida yomhlathi. Imisebenzi kule bar yesixhobo iquka ubuso obukhulu nokubhaliweyo okukekeleyo, okubhaliweyo okushicilelwe phezulu, kwaye nokudibanisa umda kumhlathi wakho</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><link linkend="file-toolbar"
>Ibar yesixhobo yefayile</link
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Ibar yesixhobo isetyenziswa ukulayisha, ukugcina, ukushicilela kunye nokuqala amaxwebhu amatsha</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><link linkend="insert-toolbar"
>Faka ibar yesixhobo</link
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Le bar yesixhobo isetyenziswa ukudibanisa izakhelo zokubhaliweyo ezintsha kuxwebhu lakho. ungadibanisa kwakhona imizobo, iindlela zokwenza imigca okanye iifomula kuxwebhu lakho ngale bar yesixhobo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><link linkend="basic-edit-toolbar"
>Hlela ibar yesixhobo</link
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Le bar yesixhobo yeyemisebenzi yokuhlela eqhelekileyo enjengoku sika, cola, sukwenza, yenza kwakhona, fumana nokhangelo lopelo</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><link linkend="paragraph-toolbar"
>Ibar yesixhobo yomhlathi</link
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Le bar yesixhobo isetyenziswa ukufaka imifanekiso, clip-=art okanye abasebenzi abathile kuxwebhu lakho.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><link linkend="table-edit-toolbar"
>Ibar yesixhobo yetafile</link
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Le bar yesixhobo isetyenziswa ukudibanisa okanye ukususa imiqolo okanye imihlathi kwiindlela zokwenza imigca.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><link linkend="border-toolbar"
>Ibar yesixhobo yemida</link
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Le bar yesixhobo isetyenziswa ukudibanisa okanye ukususa imida ejikeleze imihlathi.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><link linkend="formula-toolbar"
>Ibar yesixhobo yefomula</link
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Le bar yesixhobo isetyenziswa ukudibanisa okanye ukususa iifomula kunye namaqela wayo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> </variablelist>

</sect1>

<sect1 id="rulers">
<title
>Usebenzisa abaphathi</title>

<para
>Ngase khohlo nakwimida ephezulu we ariya yexwebhu, angumphathe othe tye kunye nothe nkqo.</para>

<para
>Aba baphathi balinganisela ukusuka entla kumda osekhohlo wephepha. </para>

<para
>Umphathi ngamnye une ariya eqaqambileyo ejikelezwe yi ariya emnyama. I ariya eqaqambileyo ibonisa ubungakanani kunye nendawo yesakhelo esikhethiweyo ngoku kwelo phepha. Xa utshintsha izakhelo, i ariya eqaqambileyo iyatshintsha ukubonisa izicwangciso zesakhelo ezintsha.</para>

<screenshot>
<mediaobject>
<imageobject>
<imagedata fileref="ruler.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject>
</mediaobject>
</screenshot>

<para
>Umphathi angalinganisela iphepha kwiminqongo emithathu yokulinganisela:</para>

<orderedlist numeration="arabic"
> <listitem
><para
>iiMillimeta (mm)</para
></listitem
> <listitem
><para
>Iincopho (pt)</para
></listitem
> <listitem
><para
>Ii-intshi (ngaphakathi)</para
></listitem
> </orderedlist>

<para
>Ukutshintsha iminqongo yomphathi, beka isalathisi se mousengapha kwenye yabaphathi (noba yenye), kwaye nqakraza nge <mousebutton
>ekunene</mousebutton
> iqhosha kwi mouse yakho.</para>

<para
>Khetha udidi lwakho kwi menu-esezantsi. Uzakuqwalasela ukuba abaphathi bobabini batshintshela kumnqongo omtsha womlinganiselo.</para>

<para
>Ungaqwalasela kwakhona iintolo ezimbini ezithe nkqo (enye yalathe phezulu, enye yalathe phantsi), kwicala lasekhohlo lwe ariya eqaqambileyo yomlawuli othe tye. Ezi zisetyenziswa ukunyenyisa umda womhlathi. Xa ufuna ulwazi oluphangaleleyo, bona icandelo elingenawonga <link linkend="format-para"
>Ifomata imihlathi.</link
></para>

<para
>Okokugqibela, ungabona amaphawu amnyama, angeyonxenye yomphathi. TAnokuvela njengemilo ka L, Ebuyiselwayo-L, uphantsi-phezulu T, okanye uphantsi-phezulu T ngechaphaza kuyo. Ezi zindawo zesithuba zokumisa. Xa ufuna ulwazi oluphangaleleyo bona icandelo elingenawonga <link linkend="tab-stops"
>Usebenzisa izithuba zokumisa</link
>.</para>

<tip
> <para
>Ukufomata ngokukhawuleza ubeko lwephepha, unganqakraza ekunene imouse noba kukowuphi umphathi. Encinane imenu esezantsi izakuvela. Khetha ngokulula ubeko lwephepha, kwaye ibhokisi yencoko yababini yobeko lwephepha izakuvela. Khetha ngokulula ubeko lwephepha, kwaye ibhokisi yencoko yababini yobeko lwephepha izakuvela.</para
> </tip>

<note
> <para
>Ukuba awufuni abaphathi kuxwebhu lakho le ariya, banoku cinywa.</para
><para
> Khetha ngokulula <menuchoice
> <guimenu
>Izicwangciso</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Qwalasela Kword</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
> kwi Menu Bar. Nqakraza ku <guibutton
>Ujongano</guibutton
> iqhosha. Ibhokisi yokukhangela ephezulu izakukuvumela uqhoboshe abaphathi ukuqala nokuyeka.</para
> </note>

</sect1>

